title: Kim Kardashian Gets Her Hair Done by North, Shares Sweet Photos of Saint in Costa Rica
text: Kim Kardashian Gets Her Hair Done by North, Shares Sweet Photos of Saint in Costa Rica by Jennifer Drysdale 2:08 PM PST, February 07, 2017 Playing Kim Kardashian Gets Her Hair Done by North, Shares Sweet Photos of Saint in Costa Rica Kim Kardashian has a new hairstylist! The 36-year-old reality star took to Snapchat on Tuesday to show off a beautiful new 'do, courtesy of her daughter, North West. WATCH: Kim Kardashian Wants Husband Kanye West to Headline Next Year's Super Bowl Halftime Show "Thank you for doing my hair so beautifully. Oh, but you left this crown in," Kardashian says in one snap, as 3-year-old Nori plays with her mom's hair. "Ah! Be gentle!" A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 7, 2017 at 8:55am PST A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 7, 2017 at 9:00am PST WATCH: Kim Kardashian Rocks Velvet Track Suit and Beige Trench Coat for Dinner Date With Kourtney "You look so pretty," North says in another video, as Kardashian shows off her understated new hairstyle. A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 7, 2017 at 9:03am PST WATCH: Kim Kardashian Reveals How Her Late Father, Kids Inspired Book Club Pick While Kardashian spends a little mommy-and-me time with her daughter, she also shared some adorable pics with her son, 1-year-old Saint, on her app. In throwback snaps from her Costa Rica vacation, the Selfish author sweetly plays with her baby boy in the water. Photo: KimKardashianWest.com
